    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Squeeze the pouch[es] of <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es] (just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two or more pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
