    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Once hot, tear your<strong> flat white mushrooms</strong> into large pieces, add them to the pan and cook for 2 min</p>",
