    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the flat white mushrooms are cooking, combine your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
